<h1>Build a Website</h1>

<section>
<h2>Problem Statement</h2>
<p>The goal of this project is to build a website that compares Spanish and English. The website should allow users to input text in either language and see a translation in the other language. The website should also include a dictionary of common words and phrases in both languages.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Design</h2>
<ul>
<li>The website will be built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.</li>
<li>The website will be hosted on GitHub Pages.</li>
<li>The website will be responsive and mobile-friendly.</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section>
<h2>User Experience Considerations</h2>
<ul>
<li>The website will be easy to use and navigate.</li>
<li>The website will be visually appealing and engaging.</li>
<li>The website will be accessible to users of all abilities.</li>
</ul>
</section>

</body>

